data.description: VA loan assumption at 3.75%. The Villa on Eaton Square. Pet friendly. Ala Moana Beach Park and sunset views. Rooftop deck, BBQ, heated pool, and gym, with 360-degree island views and Friday fireworks. In-unit washer & dryer. HOA includes electricity, AC, water, sewer, and trash. One unassigned parking in a controlled access garage with a storage locker. The building offers a commercial side with a grocery store, bakery, restaurants, and massage parlor, among other convenience establishments. ABC store & 7Eleven 1 block away. Waikiki shops, bars, restaurants, and nightlife within walking distance. Ala Moana Mall/Ala Moana Beach Park/Magic Island/Ft Derussy Beach/Hale Koa Hotel/Hawaiian Hilton Village/Lagoon fireworks, within walking distance. 24 hr security.
